## Best Practices

- Use environment variables for all secrets
- Enable SSL/HTTPS
- Use managed database (not Docker)
- Use cloud storage (S3) for file uploads
- Enable caching
- Set up error tracking (Sentry)
- Configure email delivery
- Use CDN for assets
- Enable logging
- Monitor performance

